1. a can do a work in 6 days
   b can do a work in 4 days
   how many days a and b together do a work?
1/x=1/4+1/6
1/x=3+2/12
1/x=5/12
x=12/5
answer:12/5 days

2. a can do a work in 10 days
   a+b together do a work  in 5 days
   in  how many days  b can complete it?
1/10+b=1/5
1/b=1/5-1/10
1/b=2-1/10
b=10
answer: 10 days
